Package pattpack.expr_intr

Interface Summary
Expr This class represents an expression of the "while" language.
 

Class Summary
Add This class represents an addition expression.
Div This class represents an division expression.
Gt This class represents an "greater then" conditional expression.
Lt This class represents an "less then" conditional expression.
Mul This class represents an multiplication expression.
Sub This class represents an subtraction expression.
VarFactory This class is a factory for shared variables in the abstract syntax representation of programs in a "while" language.
Variable This class represents a variable in an expression.
